289
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:12,500
Ouch!

290
00:18:13,380 --> 00:18:14,240
Oww!

291
00:18:16,840 --> 00:18:17,480
Ouch!

292
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:23,700
Hey! Don't hit me!

293
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:26,540
Even my parents never did that!

294
00:18:31,660 --> 00:18:33,120
Say something.

295
00:18:34,620 --> 00:18:36,660
Kids need discipline.

296
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,800
Do you even realize what you did?

297
00:18:42,820 --> 00:18:43,780
I...

298
00:18:43,789 --> 00:18:44,773
If I wasn't there,

299
00:18:44,781 --> 00:18:46,218
what would've happened?

300
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:53,340
Sorry.

301
00:18:53,560 --> 00:18:55,000
I don't need apologies.

302
00:19:00,360 --> 00:19:02,240
I'm asking you if you understand.

303
00:19:06,560 --> 00:19:08,340
Do you want to throw your future away?

304
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:11,022
Any idiot should be able to

305
00:19:11,038 --> 00:19:12,186
figure it out if he thinks

306
00:19:12,211 --> 00:19:13,304
about it a little.

307
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:16,025
Even if they know it's an illegal race,

308
00:19:16,050 --> 00:19:17,736
people will still turn a blind eye,

309
00:19:17,860 --> 00:19:19,266
which means the organizer

310
00:19:19,274 --> 00:19:20,954
is a dangerous person.

311
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:23,558
It's not hard to make

312
00:19:23,583 --> 00:19:24,668
an idiot disappear.

313
00:19:26,940 --> 00:19:29,920
- I didn't know...
- Not only that.

314
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,120
For adults,

315
00:19:33,040 --> 00:19:35,054
apologizing and crying about it

316
00:19:35,078 --> 00:19:36,758
won't make up for it.

317
00:19:39,800 --> 00:19:40,880
Don't be naive.

318
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,809
You are also participating

319
00:19:43,834 --> 00:19:45,354
in an illegal race!

320
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:48,080
You protected for me just now...

321
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:49,740
Aren't you in trouble?

322
00:19:49,740 --> 00:19:51,107
I will take responsibility

323
00:19:51,132 --> 00:19:52,263
for my own choices.

324
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:56,180
Because it is underground racing,

325
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:59,895
it is a place where people

326
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:01,747
want to risk their lives,

327
00:20:02,940 --> 00:20:04,224
and who want to master

328
00:20:04,255 --> 00:20:06,255
the art of maintenance.

329
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:08,240
As a mechanic,

330
00:20:08,560 --> 00:20:09,711
I think learning from

331
00:20:09,735 --> 00:20:11,360
underground racing is useful.

332
00:20:15,740 --> 00:20:17,661
I am prepared to pay

333
00:20:17,686 --> 00:20:19,366
for something important.

334
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:33,560
I didn't mean to give you any trouble,

335
00:20:35,060 --> 00:20:36,480
I just wanted revenge,

336
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:38,800
that's all.

337
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:43,180
Idiot.

338
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:47,389
All you ever do is call me an idiot!

339
00:20:47,405 --> 00:20:48,693
Is that all you can say?

340
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,820
I'm an idiot anyway.

341
00:20:51,312 --> 00:20:54,012
You're right, I am unable to think!

342
00:20:58,060 --> 00:20:59,286
Don't think I'm going to let you

343
00:20:59,310 --> 00:21:00,670
get away with it.

344
00:21:02,360 --> 00:21:03,400
Watch me,

345
00:21:04,040 --> 00:21:05,760
I'm going to make you fall for me.

346
00:21:06,580 --> 00:21:08,360
And don't call me stupid anymore.

347
00:21:26,120 --> 00:21:27,280
I'm waiting.

348
00:21:30,040 --> 00:21:31,560
Keep your promise.

349
00:21:39,180 --> 00:21:40,380
Stay the night.

350
00:21:41,420 --> 00:21:42,260
Huh?

351
00:21:52,700 --> 00:21:56,920
This way, there's no way to turn back...

352
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:09,040
Trying to make me fall in love?

353
00:22:12,860 --> 00:22:14,080
Fall in love?

354
00:22:21,140 --> 00:22:22,720
Yay!

355
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:24,420
- Whoa!
- Go!

356
00:22:30,180 --> 00:22:32,260
Wait, that's not Arashi.

357
00:22:32,460 --> 00:22:33,660
A win's a win!

358
00:22:33,784 --> 00:22:35,104
Thanks, man!

359
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:44,900
They're truly amateurs.

360
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:46,869
None of them can even hope

361
00:22:46,885 --> 00:22:48,165
to challenge me.

362
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:52,480
No matter how we compete, I'll win.

363
00:22:52,580 --> 00:22:54,540
Why don't you prove it, then?

364
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:58,680
Did you just say that?

365
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:00,598
You can bet on anything

366
00:23:00,614 --> 00:23:01,463
on tonight's match.

367
00:23:01,488 --> 00:23:04,020
Whatever you want, be it money,

368
00:23:04,380 --> 00:23:06,460
fame, or lover.

369
00:23:06,460 --> 00:23:10,460
Fuma! Come hang out with us tonight!

370
00:23:10,460 --> 00:23:12,620
Wow, that's great suggestion.

371
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:14,440
But sorry,

372
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:16,560
I have something to do today.

373
00:23:16,760 --> 00:23:18,340
Huh, why?

374
00:23:18,340 --> 00:23:19,200
Were you angry just now?

375
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:21,360
- Can't you go?
- Sorry.

376
00:23:21,720 --> 00:23:25,100
(Are you okay?
Not in danger, right?)

