379
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:09,480
“Not Just the Rain, but the Storm Approaches”

380
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:12,620
"Love in The Air -Premonition of Love -"

381
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:15,980
Did I accidentally fall asleep?

382
00:24:25,080 --> 00:24:28,120
You're so good-looking it's annoying.

383
00:24:46,680 --> 00:24:48,060
Serves you right.

384
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:52,980
Good night.
